<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>279</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hi vawlei ah Jesuh lawng nih, Vailam a put lai maw? Mikip ca put awk a
 um ko, Keica zong a um ve.

[V2]
 Vailamtahnak cu ka put lai, Thihnak caan ka phak tiang, Cun Bawi
 luchin cu kaa chinh lai, Ka inn ka phak tikah.

[V3]
 An khenhmi Jesuh ke-hram ah, Thlalang lung phah cungah, Ka sui luchin
 cu ka chiah lai, A min ka thangthat lai.

[V4]
 Maw vailam sung! Maw sui luchin! A lianngan thawhthan ni, Vancungmi
 hna rung tum tuah u, Ka thlarau kai pi u.</lyrics>
<key>A</key>
<title>JESUH LAWNG NIH MAW VAILAM A PUT LAI? CH279</title>
</song>